author: John Wildermuth
title: Jeb Bush stops in Pacific Heights for donations, draws protesters
text: Former Florida Gov. Jeb Bush was in the Bay Area on Tuesday, hoping to polish his tech connections — and grab some campaign cash — for his underperforming GOP presidential run.
